{"tid":2028781,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"水壩潰堤疏散上萬人","createTime":"2020-05-22T03:39:00.000Z","updateTime":"2020-05-22T03:51:40.000Z","uid":159448,"like":0,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"9295bd22e5c4d5e3e29a6098bf8964a88945526c","tid":2028781,"uid":159448,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-22T03:39:00.000Z","msg":"因連日豪雨，美國密西根州2座水壩潰堤，當局緊急疏散上萬居民，州長惠特梅爾（Gretchen Whitmer）宣佈米德蘭郡（Midland）進入緊急狀態，她表示，市區淹水高度可能會接近9英尺（2.7公尺）。<br />\n<br />\n綜合外媒報導，密西根州的艾登維爾（Edenville）和桑福德（Sanford）2座水壩發生「災難性的潰堤」，美國國家氣象局19日晚間呼籲，住在河川下游的居民應前往高處避難。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n距離桑福德水壩下游約12.8公里，人口約4萬2千人的米德蘭郡首當其衝，將面臨著嚴重的洪水威脅，惠特梅爾表示，「在接下來12至15個小時內，米德蘭市區可能浸泡在約9英尺深的水中。」<br />\n<br />\n在不到24小時內，當局已2次命令沿著提塔巴瓦西河（Tittabawassee River）的住家和米德蘭郡部分地區的居民撤離。惠特梅爾也不忘呼籲，民眾在避難時仍應採取措施來預防武漢肺炎疫情傳播，例如戴上口罩和保持社交距離。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.ltn.com.tw/news/world/breakingnews/3171858\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.ltn.com.tw%2Fnews%2Fworld%2Fbreakingnews%2F3171858&d=ppuFFh6piFuOrul45s7BzUYnXQRGGZgEWtwyrMN1cgk%3D&h=8d001145\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.ltn.com.tw%2Fnews%2Fworld%2Fbreakingnews%2F3171858&h=b3916dae\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.ltn.com.tw/news/world/breakingnews/3171858</a>"},{"pid":"87c4b41ea7cc3bfa31fb04fb0c0c0cd34aa8d4ac","tid":2028781,"uid":27432,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-22T03:40:24.000Z","msg":"美國多難"},{"pid":"77cb9ce9eba23c1e1a646c1bab1f168efbf3bc6a","tid":2028781,"uid":213877,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-22T03:42:58.000Z","msg":"捐錢啦，美國喔"},{"pid":"81f2b5aef3a42fbcd12485838ddd23fb26d51adc","tid":2028781,"uid":159448,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-22T03:50:39.000Z","msg":"點解唔係三峽<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/notcry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"26dda256da882b8680feabd7b0ace275ba614354","tid":2028781,"uid":357030,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"reply